{"id": 57873, "date": "2025-07-29T04:00:40", "date_gmt": "2025-07-29T11:00:40", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57873"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T12:30:25", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T19:30:25", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-29-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/29/kingdom-of-days-july-29-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 29"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1953:\u00a0</strong>Singer/songwriter and First Lady of E Street Vivienne Patricia Scialfa is born on this day in Deal, New Jersey. Happy birthday, Patti!</p>\n<p><strong>1966:\u00a0</strong>The Castiles headline at the Loew&#8217;s 35 Shore Drive-in Theater&#8217;s 10th anniversary party in Hazlet, New Jersey.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28496\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1966-07-29a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1966-07-29a.png?fit=1027%2C1398&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1027,1398\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1966-07-29a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1966-07-29a.png?fit=220%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1966-07-29a.png?fit=752%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28496 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1966-07-29a.png?resize=758%2C1032&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1032\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1966-07-29a.png?w=1027&amp;ssl=1 1027w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1966-07-29a.png?resize=220%2C300&amp;ssl=1 220w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1966-07-29a.png?resize=752%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 752w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1966-07-29a.png?resize=768%2C1045&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19970\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1966-07-29b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-07-29b.png?fit=1130%2C1315&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1130,1315\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1966-07-29b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-07-29b.png?fit=258%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-07-29b.png?fit=758%2C882&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19970 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-07-29b.png?resize=758%2C882&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"882\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-07-29b.png?w=1130&amp;ssl=1 1130w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-07-29b.png?resize=258%2C300&amp;ssl=1 258w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-07-29b.png?resize=880%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 880w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1966-07-29b.png?resize=768%2C894&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3278\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1966-0729/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1966-0729.gif?fit=253%2C147&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"253,147\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1966-0729\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1966-0729.gif?fit=253%2C147&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1966-0729.gif?fit=253%2C147&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3278 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1966-0729.gif?resize=253%2C147&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"253\" height=\"147\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1971:\u00a0</strong>The Bruce Springsteen Band plays two shows at D&#8217;Scene in South Amboy, New Jersey. The setlist includes &#8220;Natural Magic,&#8221; &#8220;Goin&#8217; Back to Georgia,&#8221; &#8220;Dance Dance Dance,&#8221; and more.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ok630L5Z9D8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Before their gig that evening at the Carter Barron Amphitheater in Washington, DC&#8217;s Rock Creek Park, Bruce stops by a local radio station for an on-air interview.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-57873-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1975-07-29_WHFS_interview_KLICKAUD.mp3?_=1\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1975-07-29_WHFS_interview_KLICKAUD.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/1975-07-29_WHFS_interview_KLICKAUD.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>1976:\u00a0</strong>Mike Appel countersues Bruce for breach of contract, escalating their legal battle.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>At the Bayfront Center Arena in St. Petersburg, Bruce opens his Darkness Tour show with his debut of &#8220;Oh Boy&#8221; and adds a second cover debut later in the show: Chuck Berry&#8217;s &#8220;Around and Around.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LOhgVbjnd84?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28498\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-07-29-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-29.png?fit=423%2C1754&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"423,1754\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-07-29\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-29.png?fit=72%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-29.png?fit=247%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28498 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-29.png?resize=423%2C1754&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"423\" height=\"1754\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-29.png?w=423&amp;ssl=1 423w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-29.png?resize=72%2C300&amp;ssl=1 72w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1978-07-29.png?resize=247%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 247w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19973\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-07-29b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1978-07-29b.png?fit=1651%